{
  "stem": "19596.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in-- in Auschwitz, there was no-- no seniority of Jews at all.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were all that nationality, or German criminals which were in charge, like oberkapos, green-- green-- you see, there was a difference between green triangle and red triangle.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The red triangle were political, where the green triangle were criminals.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was sleeping in a very good block, with people which had already good kommandos.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We call them kommandos, working kommandos.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We all had our little wardrobe even, our little cupboards, where we can lock in our food and our personal belongings.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have to keep it under the mattress, like in other barracks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went to work at-- after the-- after the roll call at 6 o'clock, we went to work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Went to work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had a-- a [INAUDIBLE] which is-- which is a role who irons the clothing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had washing troughs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We boiled the laundry in copper-- in copper-- big copper kettles with wooden sticks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had soap.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had everything in there, at work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had drying cupboards and drying rooms where we're drying the-- the laundry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we are working exclusively for the SS administration and SS in charge.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not by myself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I always had somebody to deliver and I had a guard behind me, outside every time you go outside the gates, you had to report and things were written, time-- the time and who passes and what number passes and where you're going.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then when you come in, you had to be in at a certain time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the SS barracks, they were outside the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the barracks, outside the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you go further in the camp, we call it the [NON-ENGLISH] was 50 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a second-- a second security guards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
